reviews.text:
There are lots of bars in Lan Kwai Fong, but this one I think their drinks aren't so particular to me. Just for tourists who haven't been here, so you know...
BTW, I know lots of places received credit cards, Alipay, Octopus in Hong Kong, so I did not bring any cash that day, the staff lady was unwilling to let us use VISA card when we checked out. Come on, this is the era of mobile payment!
Nice and friendly staff with good cocktails
